女王迁离伦敦，10万民众请愿！英国卫生大臣回应“群体免疫”：不是你们想的那样。
The Queen has moved out of London and 100,000 people have petitioned! The British Health Secretary has responded to "mass immunization": not what you think.
中国经营报                      。
China Business News.
中国经营报。
